==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intersection
<hw>In`ter*sec"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>intersectio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>intersection</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act, state, or place of intersecting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Geom.)</fld> <def>The point or line in which one
line or surface cuts another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intersectional</ent>⟦br⟧
